---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base title="Partner with AI Companion Today — Sponsored Placements & Brand Collaborations" description="Reach an engaged audience of AI companion app buyers, mental-health-app researchers, AgeTech decision makers and productivity AI users. Sponsored reviews, newsletter placements and category takeovers." canonical="https://aicompaniontoday.com/partner/">
  <section class="py-16 max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6">
    <span class="text-xs bg-accent text-white px-3 py-1 rounded-full font-sans font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider">For brands & networks</span>
    <h1 class="text-5xl font-bold text-primary mt-4 mb-6 tracking-tight font-sans">Partner with AI Companion Today</h1>
    <p class="text-xl text-ink leading-relaxed mb-10">AI Companion Today reaches an engaged, purchase-ready audience across seven AI verticals. We work with app publishers, AI platforms, affiliate networks and brands on transparent sponsored placements that respect our editorial firewall.</p>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-12">
      <div class="bg-white border border-surface-border rounded-xl p-6">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-primary mb-3 font-sans">Who reads AICT</h2>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-ink">
          <li>AI companion app buyers (B2C consumer)</li>
          <li>Mental-health app researchers and caregivers</li>
          <li>AgeTech decision-makers (families, eldercare facilities)</li>
          <li>Language learners shopping premium tiers</li>
          <li>Prosumers evaluating AI productivity stacks</li>
          <li>Romance / adult AI shoppers (18+, age-gated section)</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-white border border-surface-border rounded-xl p-6">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-primary mb-3 font-sans">Topics we cover</h2>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-ink">
          <li>Best-of guides (ranked, scored)</li>
          <li>Head-to-head comparisons</li>
          <li>Hands-on reviews (14-30 day testing)</li>
          <li>Methodology-driven category analyses</li>
          <li>Monthly "State of AI Companion" reports</li>
          <li>Buyer education and matcher tools</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-primary mb-6 font-sans">Placement formats</h2>
    <div class="space-y-4 mb-12">
      <div class="bg-white border border-surface-border rounded-xl p-6">
        <h3 class="font-bold text-primary text-lg mb-2 font-sans">Sponsored review / deep dive</h3>
        <p class="text-ink leading-relaxed">Long-form editorial with full testing methodology applied. Clearly labelled as sponsored. Includes fair-use pros and cons; we will not fabricate scoring. Typical timeline: 4-6 weeks.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-white border border-surface-border rounded-xl p-6">
        <h3 class="font-bold text-primary text-lg mb-2 font-sans">Newsletter placement</h3>
        <p class="text-ink leading-relaxed">Featured spot in our weekly newsletter delivered to subscribers who opted in for AI companion updates. Includes brand logo, tagline, CTA, and short editorial intro.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-white border border-surface-border rounded-xl p-6">
        <h3 class="font-bold text-primary text-lg mb-2 font-sans">Category takeover</h3>
        <p class="text-ink leading-relaxed">Featured across a full vertical landing page for 30 days. Exclusive or co-presented with one competitor only. Best for platforms launching a new tier or geo expansion.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-white border border-surface-border rounded-xl p-6">
        <h3 class="font-bold text-primary text-lg mb-2 font-sans">Affiliate network inclusion</h3>
        <p class="text-ink leading-relaxed">If you operate an affiliate program on CrakRevenue, Impact, Awin, or a direct program, we route relevant traffic through our /go tracking layer with postback analytics and segmented sub-IDs.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-white border border-surface-border rounded-xl p-6">
        <h3 class="font-bold text-primary text-lg mb-2 font-sans">Matcher quiz integration</h3>
        <p class="text-ink leading-relaxed">Add your app to our <a href="/tools/matcher/" class="text-accent hover:underline">AI Companion Matcher</a> scoring matrix with a verified app profile. Qualified leads matched to your platform redirect through tracked CTAs.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-primary mb-6 font-sans">Our editorial firewall</h2>
    <div class="bg-surface-alt border border-surface-border rounded-xl p-6 mb-12">
      <ul class="space-y-3 text-ink">
        <li><strong>Rankings are independent.</strong> Commission size never moves an app up or down our ranked lists.</li>
        <li><strong>Paid content is labelled.</strong> Sponsored reviews carry a clear disclosure at the top of the article and in the URL slug.</li>
        <li><strong>YMYL rules apply.</strong> Mental-health content follows strict safety guardrails; we will decline placements that could harm vulnerable users.</li>
        <li><strong>No fabricated scores.</strong> We publish our 12-criteria grid; your score is your score.</li>
        <li><strong>Mutual approval before publish.</strong> You review the draft; we retain final editorial control.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-primary mb-6 font-sans">Get in touch</h2>
    <div class="bg-white border-2 border-primary rounded-xl p-8">
      <p class="text-lg text-ink leading-relaxed mb-6">Email us with your placement ask, expected budget range, timing and a brief description of your platform. We reply within 3 business days.</p>
      <p class="text-xl font-mono mb-6"><a href="mailto:press@aicompaniontoday.com?subject=Partnership%20inquiry" class="text-accent hover:underline">press@aicompaniontoday.com</a></p>
      <p class="text-sm text-ink-muted font-sans">Please include: <strong>company name</strong>, <strong>product URL</strong>, <strong>placement type</strong>, <strong>timeline</strong>, <strong>target geo</strong>.</p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>
